author: Second Wind
description:
Blood Typers is a multiplayer survival horror indie game where every single action is done by typing words on your keyboard.

Blood Typers releases on Steam on February 20th, 2025, and you can play the demo today — https://store.steampowered.com/app/2790330/Blood_Typers/
